Miscellaneous Order.

No. 590. Pannell v. United States. David Berger and Thomas D. McBride for petitioner. Solicitor General Perlman, Assistant Attorney General Caudle and Ellis N. Slack for the United States. Reported below: 178 F. 2d 98.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Third Circuit dismissed on motion of counsel for the petitioner.
